Everybody dreams of experiencing that rush of adrenaline when you stand atop of a hillock and watch those trees swaying while the water flows down a beautiful stream. Prepare yourself for one such expedition by packing your belongings in the Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack. This backpack can be used by both men and women.

Body

This backpack is made of 210D Nylon Ripstop and 420D Nylon Dobby which lend it robustness and durability. The dimensions given to this bag are 279.4 x 482.6 x 152.4 mm in dimension this backpack compact but can accommodate all your essentials with ease. Weighing 560 g this bag is lightweight and easy to carry around. With a 20 litre carrying capacity this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack can accommodate all your essentials such as clothes accessories and equipment without much trouble.

Features

Equipped with three compartments and two pockets this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. Keeping your load in place and preventing it from shifting around unnecessarily are the sternum straps of this backpack. Ensuring you are comfortable while moving around are the padded shoulder straps and back. Facilitating easy portability of this backpack is the reinforced haul loop which can be used when you don’t want to strap it on. Giving you visibility when it is dark is the reflector tape on this bag. To ensure that you don’t have to stop every time you want a drink of water this backpack has a hydration bladder compartment and straps for holding hydration bladder. As this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack is bar tacked on specialised machines it is resilient to common damages like tearing and ripping.

Life can be stressful at times and to beat the pressure all you need to do is hit the road and discover an unknown destination this will let your mind and body free of all those worldly holds. Pack your belongings in the Wildcraft Pack Y 28 L Backpack and take control of the steering wheel. This bag has been designed for both men and women.

Body

Made of 210D Nylon Double Ripstop and 420D Nylon Dobby this backpack is durable and resistant to common damages like tearing and ripping. Measuring 330.2 x 508 x 177.8 mm in dimension this backpack boasts of a slender profile but can fit in all your essentials with ease. Weighing 560 g this bag is lightweight and can be carried around with ease. With a carrying capacity of 28 litres this backpack can accommodate your clothes eatables equipment and other accessories without much trouble.

Features

A good backpack is equipped with multiple features which help you carry your belongings and at the same time ensure that your comfort is not compromised on. Equipped with two compartments and three pockets this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. The side air mesh pockets of this backpack are where you can keep your water bottle or other small accessories. Ensuring that you are relaxed while discovering a new place are the padded shoulder straps and back which provide you with a comfortable carrying experience. For the load management this backpack has been furnished with compression straps at the top and bottom. You can slip in some snacks or accessories in the front flat zippered mesh pocket of this Wildcraft Pack Y 28 L Backpack. This bag has specially designed channels on the back which facilitate a sufficient flow of air. As this backpack is bar tacked on specialised machines it is robust and sure to last you for a longer time. Keeping all your possessions safely encased within are the zipper and buckle closure of this bag.
